{
  "stem": "24650.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I tell you, the-- the how do you call it, the place where in Ponary, my friend made that was written about that here was killed 360,000 people in Hebrew and in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they take it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody from the government [INAUDIBLE] the-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Police, somebody-- you can't--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They changed what was written, that here are lying people killed by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was two cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one cemetery-- a holy man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was Christian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he changed for Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], his son, and they took his-- they burned him alive in-- in the city, the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they took the-- when a person burned, what comes out?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ashes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ashes, like in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put it in a grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it grows-- did grow a tree like a person-- hand, feet, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They left it be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know, the Lithuanian or the Russian, they closed both cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No cemeteries anymore, houses-- new houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did it in Kiev, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I settled where my husband was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he got to know that his mother and two sisters are alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, what will we go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's sit here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, we sit. 10 years of the 12 and a half, I was most of the time hungry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, because he worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you couldn't make a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because if you get 350 gram bread, then you need 600.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you don't have fat.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
